#Pre-requisits

* Ubuntu 10.04 machine

## Setting up an Ubuntu dev machine using Virtual Box

* Download VirtualBox - https://www.virtualbox.org/wiki/Downloads
* Install Ubuntu 10.04 LTS server edition (32 or 64bit) - https://help.ubuntu.com/community/Installation/MinimalCD
* Change the network mode to "Bridged adapter"
* Do not install any additional packages on Ubuntu; the wordpress-in-a-box scripts will do all this for you
* install SSH - sudo apt-get install ssh

# Configuring a machine
1. SSH into your Ubuntu machine
1. sudo apt-get install git-core python-pip python-dev
1. sudo pip install littlechef
1. cd ~
1. git clone git://github.com/mrdavidlaing/wordpress-in-a-box.git
1. 


